#: kb/admin.py:2623
msgid "Controls authentication/MFA logs, general activity logs, admin log display rows, and user session lifetime. Default log retention is 30 days. Admin log tables show 200 rows per page by default. Sessions default to 8 hours and can be set from 1 to 168 hours."
